// Computing leap years with "pure" clocks and filtering

int-clock year periodic 1

unit-clock year4
year every 4 implies year4

unit-clock year100
year4 every 25 implies year100

unit-clock year400
year100 every 4 implies year400

unit-clock leap
// A year is leap if it is divisible by 4 but not by 100
year4 when not year100 implies leap
// However, a year divisible by 400 is leap
year400 implies leap

@maxstep 2200
//@trace info
@output svg xscale 30 standalone
